MOST IMME
No. 1/34/1/2012-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 10th August, 2012
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 10th August, 2012:
Shri Vilasrao Deshmukh relinquished the charge of (a) the office of the Minister of
(i)
Science and Technology, and the Minister of Earth Sciences; and (b) the additional
charge of the office of the Minister of Micro, Small and Medium Enterprises. He
assumed the charge of the Minister without Portfolio.
Shri Vayalar Ravi assumed the additional charge of the office of (a) the Minister of
Science and Technology, (b) the Minister of Earth Sciences; and (c) the Minister of
Micro, Small and Medium Enterprises. He will continue to hold the charge of the office
of the Minister of Overseas Indian Affairs.
(ii)
